{"tid":2148074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度南部收治新型肺炎患者酒店火警 至少10死","createTime":"2020-08-09T16:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T16:58:17.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15616b05052d1c67507b494543b788aec8279006","tid":2148074,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"印度南部收治新型肺炎患者酒店火警 至少10死<br />\n2020-08-09 HKT 21:12<br />\n<br />\n&quot;印度南部用於收治新型肺炎患者的酒店，當地周日凌晨火警，造成至少10人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發安得拉邦維傑亞瓦達市，當地凌晨約5時，住有新型肺炎患者的一家酒店起火，共有患者和醫護人員約40人。大火撲滅後，搜救人員救出20人，並轉移至附近醫院。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542741-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542741-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=788ae711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542741-20200809.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=643d9291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542741-20200809.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">禍不單行<br />\nRIP</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"871c0435bcf310e01032e659bbe0da05ef663786","tid":2148074,"uid":23162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"應該有預謀，班㗎喱係生蕃嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579ef26c36f4c827b88edc46e6c5ea73b32985ea","tid":2148074,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T16:58:17.000Z","msg":"用濃煙殺死武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}